---
import ContentPage from './ContentPage.astro';
---

<ContentPage title="Пример инвойса">
  <p class="intro">
    Шаблон инвойса, который можно использовать для выписывания иностранной компании.
    Включает все необходимые поля: реквизиты ИП, описание услуг, сумму, банковские реквизиты для международного перевода (SWIFT/IBAN).
  </p>

  <p>
    <a href="/files/invoice-template.docx" download class="download-link">
      <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
        <path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4"></path>
        <polyline points="7 10 12 15 17 10"></polyline>
        <line x1="12" y1="15" x2="12" y2="3"></line>
      </svg>
      Скачать шаблон инвойса (.docx, 9 КБ)
    </a>
  </p>

  <h2>Пример заполнения</h2>

  <div class="invoice-preview">
    <div class="invoice-header">
      <h3 class="invoice-title">Invoice #20240305_13</h3>
    </div>

    <div class="invoice-section">
      <div class="invoice-parties">
        <div class="invoice-party">
          <p class="invoice-label">From:</p>
          <p><strong>Individual Entrepreneur John Doe</strong></p>
          <p>Address: Kazakhstan, 050000, Almaty, Maulenov 125, aprt.13</p>
          <p>Tel.: +7 (701) 762-00-00</p>
          <p>Registration number: KZ75UWQ02408999</p>
          <p>Identification number: 931019300788</p>
        </div>
        <div class="invoice-party">
          <p class="invoice-label">To:</p>
          <p><strong>&lt;CompanyName&gt; LLC</strong></p>
          <p>Address: Address</p>
          <p>City: City</p>
          <p>Country: Country</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="invoice-section">
      <table class="data-table">
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>#</th>
            <th>Services description</th>
            <th>Period of services</th>
            <th>Total cost (USD)</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td class="cell-center">1</td>
            <td>Software development services</td>
            <td>April, 2025</td>
            <td class="cell-mono">0</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>

    <div class="invoice-section">
      <p class="invoice-label">Payment details:</p>
      <p>Software development services according to Agreement #20240305 dated March 5, 2024.</p>
      <p><strong>Amount:</strong> 0 000 USD (Zero thousands USD 00 cents), no VAT.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="invoice-section">
      <p class="invoice-label">Terms of payments and acceptation:</p>
      <p>Postpayment of 100% upon the services delivery in accordance with the Services Agreement.
      By full payment of this invoice the &lt;CompanyName&gt; confirms, that all the contract conditions
      listed below have been utterly fulfilled in due time and with adequate quality.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="invoice-section">
      <p class="invoice-label">Bank details:</p>
      <p><strong>Account with Institution:</strong> JSC Halyk Bank</p>
      <p><strong>SWIFT:</strong> HSBKKZKX</p>
      <p>40 Al-Farabi ave., A26M3K5, Almaty, Kazakhstan</p>
      <p><strong>Beneficiary account:</strong> KZ98601A861003281100</p>
      <p><strong>Beneficiary:</strong> John Doe</p>
    </div>

    <div class="invoice-section invoice-signature">
      <p>John Doe: ___________________________________________________________</p>
      <p>Date: 2025-04-17</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2>Пояснения к полям</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Invoice #</strong> — номер инвойса, обычно формат: дата договора + порядковый номер</li>
    <li><strong>From</strong> — ваши реквизиты ИП: адрес, телефон, регистрационный номер, ИИН</li>
    <li><strong>To</strong> — реквизиты компании-заказчика</li>
    <li><strong>Services description</strong> — описание оказанных услуг</li>
    <li><strong>Period of services</strong> — период, за который оказаны услуги</li>
    <li><strong>Amount</strong> — сумма прописью и цифрами, с пометкой «no VAT» (ИП на упрощенке не платят НДС)</li>
    <li><strong>SWIFT / Beneficiary account</strong> — реквизиты вашего банковского счета для международного перевода</li>
  </ul>
</ContentPage>

<style>
  .download-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    padding: var(--space-3) var(--space-5);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-secondary);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
    color: var(--fg-primary);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: border-color var(--transition-default), background var(--transition-default);
  }

  .download-link:hover {
    border-color: var(--accent);
    background: var(--bg-tertiary);
    color: var(--fg-primary);
  }

  .invoice-preview {
    border: 1px solid var(--border-secondary);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    background: #fff;
    color: #172033;
    padding: var(--space-6);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
  }

  [data-theme='dark'] .invoice-preview {
    background: #1B2940;
    color: #EAF0F8;
  }

  .invoice-header {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-3);
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border-primary);
  }

  .invoice-title {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .invoice-section {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
  }

  .invoice-section:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .invoice-section p {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin-bottom: 2px;
  }

  .invoice-label {
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-1);
  }

  .invoice-parties {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-6);
  }

  .invoice-signature {
    padding-top: var(--space-4);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-secondary);
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .invoice-parties {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .invoice-preview {
      padding: var(--space-4);
    }
  }
</style>
